
## Task 2 Simulation Demonstration

To better illustrate how the perception system works, we have also recorded a short video showing the **Gazebo simulation and perception pipeline in action**.

The video demonstrates the following:

- The simulated chess board environment in Gazebo  
- Detection of ArUco markers from the camera view  
- Mapping of detected markers to board coordinates  
- Reconstruction of the 6 × 6 board configuration  

This video provides a clearer understanding of how the perception module processes visual input and converts it into a board state that can be used by the game engine.

